* Bart Schaefer <schaefer@brasslantern.com> [2002-03-23 19:36]:
> On Mar 23,  7:56pm, Sven Guckes wrote:
> }   $ for i in 1 2 3 4 5 10 15 20 25 30 35 40 35 40 45 50; do
> }       ls *(.Lk-$i)|wc -l
> }     end
> }   zsh: parse error near `end'
